    "description": "Tokai Soft Co., Ltd. provides factory automation and embedded software development and network infrastructure technology services in Japan. The company develops industrial system, which includes artificial intelligence system development, manufacturing site improvement solution, images solution, FA system, logistics system, and product development; business system development, such as contract business development, ERP, manufacturing execution system, IoT/cloud solution, and data visualization and digitization solution; and government system development. It also offers embedded software development, comprising vending machine software development, embedded system construction technology, collaboration and project participation, and refactoring; and in-vehicle software verification, ECU software development, model-based development, and AUTOSAR platform development support. In addition, the company offers digital home appliances. Tokai Soft Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1970 and is headquartered in Nagoya, Japan."
